project_descr: Increase Youth's Awareness. Knowledge, and life skills on sexual transmitted Diseases including HIV/AIDS and reproductive Health

outputs.output_descr: Three main strategic areas of intervention: i) Peer education program on reproductive health and STIs including HIV/AIDS, ii) Community awareness building; iii) Improving of health providers awareness on youth friendly services.
donor_name: JOINT UNITED NATIONS PROGRAMME ON HIV/AIDS
